<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Course Description:</strong></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Explores adult education principles and course design for a variety of l=
earning environments. Evaluates strategies to boost learner satisfaction an=
d retention, including 'backward design.' Emphasizes key design techniques =
and online tools. Identifies methods for assessing learning outcomes. Intro=
duces the Quality Matters Rubric 5 Pillars of Quality and support resources=
 for robust course creation and teaching effectiveness. Culminates in a Pop=
ulation Health lesson plan and group work on a collaborative, ongoing class=
 project in educational technology for Population Health.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
