<p><strong>Required Texts or Other Resources:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><em>Rapid Instructional Design. 3rd Edition.</em> George M. Piskurich. <=
br>
Wiley. ISNB: 978-1118973974</p></li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Notes on Texts or Materials:</strong></p>
<p>The Piskurich textbook is available online through Scott Memorial Librar=
y: <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://jefferson.primo.exlibrisgroup=
.com/permalink/01TJU_INST/gbh139/cdi_safari_books_v2_9781118973974" rel=3D"=
nofollow">Rapid Instructional Design</a>.</p>
<p></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
<p></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"2" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Course Learning Objectives:</strong></p>
<p><em>After successfully completing this course, participants will be able=
 to:</em></p>
<p></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"aui confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">PLO-01</td>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">Develop an evidence-based lesson plan as part of an educational p=
rogram for adult learners.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">PLO-02</td>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">Identify and address the needs of critical third-party stakeholde=
rs--such as accreditors, administrators, and other reviewers or clients--al=
ong with the needs of learners.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">PLO-03</td>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">Apply the 'Backward' design approach to lesson and course develop=
ment for both online and classroom-based environments.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">PLO-04</td>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">Design and deliver an engaging presentation promoting learner sat=
isfaction, retention of knowledge, and application.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">PLO-05</td>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">Efficiently assess and evaluate the learner's experience and achi=
evement.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">PLO-06</td>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">Formulate timely, well-considered feedback and coaching to learne=
rs.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">PLO-07</td>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">Design a project in educational technology addressing a recognize=
d need in Population Health.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">PLO-08</td>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">Develop a design through Alpha, Beta, and Final stages of complet=
ion.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">PLO-09</td>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">Validate a project's design, processes, and outputs.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">PLO-10</td>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">Implement an Ed Tech project in a specified environment.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">PLO-11</td>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">Evaluate user ineractions and learning experiences in terms of a =
project's interfaces, inputs, and outputs.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">PLO-12</td>
<td style=3D"font-size: 11.0pt;font-family: Times New Roman;" class=3D"conf=
luenceTd">Continuously improve and innovate teaching through critical self-=
reflection and evidence-based practice.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
